history.content:
See information from L&S:

 Happy New Year!

I want to let you know that our office in Evans is closed this week, January 6 - 10, for ventilation work.  
We are still advising students in person or remotely.
January 6 - 7
We are in 156 Dwinelle (we are also using two conference rooms).
Hours are 9am - noon, 1pm - 4pm.
January 8
We are still in Dwinelle, but will open at 1pm.
January 9 - 10
We will be closed since we will be in training.
January 13
We will be open at both Dwinelle and Evans (see @11181 for update)
history.subject: L&S Advising Availability, January 6 - 10, 2020
